\n< Erika >Serena! Watch out!

\n< Serena >My apologies. But I'll be fine. Arrows
of that caliber can't penetrate my
Affabilis!

\n< Erika >There's a limit to everything! Tch, the
entrance is being guarded. We can't
carelessly make our move, this is bad.

...So they intend to trap us and wait
for reinforcements before attacking.
Then we can't afford to waste time. I
must find a way out...\n< Serena >

\n< Erika >...No, that's why I said I have a plan,
Serena. Let's quickly head to the loot
storage area.
\n< Serena >...Indeed.

\n< Erika >We're gonna get shot at again, Serena.
The loot storage is upstairs.
Alright, we've made it to the exit.\n< Serena >

We've managed well so far, but there
should still be some thieves left
outside.\n< Serena >

We'll probably have to fight them. Are
you ready?\n< Serena >

Ready or not doesn't matter. If we stay
here any longer, we'll die. It's do or
die once we're out.\n< Erika >
Okay, let's go!\n< Serena >
